data.description: RARE FIND! Welcome home to this peaceful slice of heaven located on 1.38 acres in the sought after town of Ponte Vedra Beach. This charming two bedroom/ one bath home provides the best of indoor / outdoor living. Enjoy beautiful views and breathtaking sunsets from one of the three porches. Live in the current home while you build a second home in the back, and then turn the current home into a rental or guest house. Endless options! The current home is situated at the front of the property providing the acreage to build behind for ultimate privacy. Zoned Open Rural with no HOA, you may own livestock, horses, park your boat or RV. Country living just miles from the beach. Boat launch / intracoastal waterway access less than 2 miles away. Top rated schools, restaurants and shopping nearby. Owner places no value on the existing structure. The 1.38 acres is the asset here. Utilities in place; new county sewer connection roadside. This is a MUST SEE! Call for your tour today.
